[normal] 
[normal]remedy.
[normal] 
[normal]You have to balance these things and ultimately I agree it is for the public to decide whether that ultimate protection of 
[normal]people
[normal]’s liberties is worth having.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Q79 [bold]&#xa0; 
