[normal] 
[normal]That is the mechanism, the system, that the Human Rights Act has introduced.
[normal] 
[normal]That is what Lord Lester said, rightly, was the British compromise that his ingenuity and the ingenuity of others had arrived at.
[normal] 
[normal]It is that mechanism, it is that system, which the Human Rights Act has 
[normal]established, which some of us are suggesting could be borrowed and extended and applied for the purposes of a codificatory system.
