[normal]Examination of Witness[bold]Witness
[normal]:
[normal] 
[normal]Nat Le Roux[bold], Director, Constitution Society, gave evidence.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Q89 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]Chair:[bold] Nat, glad to see you here.
[normal] 
[normal]Welcome.
[normal] 
[normal]Sorry that we have kept you.
[normal] 
